snippet.title: Jawan |Official Hindi Prevue |Shah Rukh Khan |Atlee |Nayanthara |Vijay Sethupathi |Deepika |Anirudh
snippet.description:
Red Chillies Entertainment presents the prevue of the highly awaited, Jawan, starring Shah Rukh Khan, Nayanthara, Vijay Sethupathi, Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance) and directed by Atlee. Jawan hits the big screens on 7th September 2023 in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu! #JawanPrevue #JawanOn7September
 
Jawan is a high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in society.

snippet.title: Gokuldham ने लगाया निशुल्क प्याऊ | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Full Episode 2444 | 1 July 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Episode 2444: 
-------------------------------------
Champaklal calls an urgent meeting at the Gokuldham society. He informs the society members about animals and humans suffering dehydration during summer. All the Gokuldham society members together decide to make amenities to quench the thirst of humans and animals.


Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 2444
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

  Gokuldham ने लगाया निशुल्क प्याऊ | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Full Episode 2444 | 1 July 2023

snippet.title: Salaar Teaser | Prabhas, Prashanth Neel, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Hombale Films, Vijay Kiragandur
snippet.description:
THE MOST VIOLENT MEN... CALLED ONE MAN... THE MOST VIOLENT 🔥
Presenting our next feature #SalaarCeaseFire to the world

From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Sep 28th,2023.

snippet.title: Bawaal - Official Trailer | Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
National Award Winners Sajid Nadiadwala & Nitesh Tiwari bring to you Bawaal on Prime Video
Presenting the official teaser of BAWAAL 
Varun Dhawan as Ajay Dixit 
Janhvi Kapoor as Nisha 
Produced by Sajid Nadiadwala 
Directed by Nitesh Tiwari 
Co-produced by Ashwiny Iyer Tiwari 
Written by Nitesh Tiwari, Nikhil Mehrotra, Piyush Gupta, Shreyas Jain, Ashwiny Iyer Tiwari 
A Nadiadwala Grandson Entertainment and EarthSky Pictures Production  
Music on T-series

Bawaal to release on Amazon Prime Video on 21st July 2023

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

#janhvikapoor #varundhawan #nadiadwalagrandson #earthskynotes #ashwinyiyertiwari #mehrotranikhil #bawlekiduniya #wardakhannadiadwala #bawaalonprime

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: PUBG Love Story : प्यार की ख़ातिर Pakistan से भारत आईं Seema ज़मानत के बाद क्या-क्या बोलीं? (BBC)
snippet.description:
भारत के ग्रेटर नोएडा में रहने वाले सचिन मीणा से प्यार करने वालीं सीमा का कहना है कि वो कभी भी लौटकर पाकिस्तान नहीं जाना चाहतीं. कराची की रहने वाली सीमा पहले शारजाह के रास्ते नेपाल पहुंचीं और नेपाल से भारत में आकर रहने लगी थीं. उन दोनों को पुलिस ने हिरासत में ले लिया था, लेकिन ज़मानत मिलने के बाद उन लोगों ने मीडिया से बातचीत की. बीबीसी टीम ने जब दोनों से मुलाकात की तो दोनों का कहना था कि सीमा लौटकर पाकिस्तान नहीं जाना चाहती. शऊदी अरब में रहने वाले सीमा के पति गुलाम हैदर ने सीमा और सचिन के बारे में काफ़ी कुछ कहा था, उस पर भी सीमा ने जवाब दिया है.

वीडियो: अभिनव गोयल और शाहनवाज़ अहमद

 #Pakistan #PUBG #indiapakistanlovestory 

सीमा हैदर के गले में 'राधे-राधे' का दुपट्टा और मंगलसूत्र, सचिन के घर में गूंजते 'जय श्री राम' के नारे- ग्राउंड रिपोर्ट

localized.description:
भारत के ग्रेटर नोएडा में रहने वाले सचिन मीणा से प्यार करने वालीं सीमा का कहना है कि वो कभी भी लौटकर पाकिस्तान नहीं जाना चाहतीं. कराची की रहने वाली सीमा पहले शारजाह के रास्ते नेपाल पहुंचीं और नेपाल से भारत में आकर रहने लगी थीं. उन दोनों को पुलिस ने हिरासत में ले लिया था, लेकिन ज़मानत मिलने के बाद उन लोगों ने मीडिया से बातचीत की. बीबीसी टीम ने जब दोनों से मुलाकात की तो दोनों का कहना था कि सीमा लौटकर पाकिस्तान नहीं जाना चाहती. शऊदी अरब में रहने वाले सीमा के पति गुलाम हैदर ने सीमा और सचिन के बारे में काफ़ी कुछ कहा था, उस पर भी सीमा ने जवाब दिया है.

वीडियो: अभिनव गोयल और शाहनवाज़ अहमद

snippet.title: “मैंने Sachin से शादी कर ली है, अब मैं पाकिस्तानी नहीं हिंदुस्तानी हूं” : जेल से छूटी Seema
snippet.description:
पाकिस्तानी महिला सीमा गुलाम हैदर (Semma Haider) और उसके भारतीय प्रेमी सचिन मीणा (Sachin Meena) को ग्रेटर नोएडा (Greater Noida) की एक अदालत ने जमानत दे दी. जमानत मिलने के बाद सीमा बेहद खुश नजर आईं. एनडीटीवी के साथ खास बातचीत में सीमा ने कहा कि अब मैं पाकिस्‍तानी नहीं, बल्कि इंडियन हूं. 

About NDTV India (Hindi News Channel): 
 
NDTV इंडिया भारत का सबसे विश्वसनीय हिन्दी न्यूज़ चैनल है, जो पॉलिटिक्स, बिज़नेस, खेल, बॉलीवुड और बहुत-से क्षेत्रों की ताज़ातरीन ख़बरें समूचे देश और दुनियाभर से आपके लिए लाता है. ख़बरों के अलावा NDTV इंडिया पर बड़ी राजनैतिक डिबेट्स, एक्सक्लूसिव इंटरव्यूज़, टॉक शोज़ भी चौबीसों घंटे लगातार चलते रहते हैं, जिनमें ढेरों भरोसेमंद जानकारी आप तक सभी प्लेटफॉर्मों - टीवी, इंटरनेट और मोबाइल - के ज़रिये पहुंचती है. 

NDTV India is a 24-hour Hindi news channel. NDTV India established its image as one of India's leading credible news channels, and is a preferred channel by an audience which favours high quality local and world news, rather than sensational infotainment. NDTV India's popular shows revolve around: news, politics, economy, sports, entertainment, panel discussions with eminent personalities and noteworthy commentaries.

Napoleon is a spectacle-filled action epic that details the checkered rise and fall of the iconic French Emperor Napoleon Bonaparte, played by Oscar®-winner Joaquin Phoenix. Against a stunning backdrop of large-scale filmmaking orchestrated by legendary director Ridley Scott, the film captures Bonaparte's relentless journey to power through the prism of his addictive, volatile relationship with his one true love, Josephine, showcasing his visionary military and political tactics against some of the most dynamic practical battle sequences ever filmed.

snippet.title: RED & WHITE DRAGON FRUIT MILKSHAKE | Easy Milkshake Recipe | Ice Cream Fruit Dessert Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we make a delicious dragon fruit milkshake recipe using Red & White Dragon Fruits. We make this milkshake recipe quick and easy, but the complex process is grinding all dragon fruit pulp in a traditional stone grinder.

We add some sugar and ice cream to make this milkshake original!

The taste is Delicious!

snippet.title: Instant Idli | అతి మృదువైన ఇడ్లి 30 నిమిషాల్లో | Soft Idli Recipe | Vismai Food
snippet.description:
Instant Idli | chawal ke aate ki idli | Instant Idli Recipe | Instant Poha Idli | idli | idli recipe | Instant | idli without idli stand | Rava idli | idli recipe in telugu | idli banane ki recipe | idli recipe in telugu | idli batter recipe | idli chutney recipe |

Hello Foodies!
Are you looking for a quick and easy breakfast recipe? Today we're going to show you how to make an extremely soft and spongy instant idli at home. This instant idli is made with simple ingredients like as poha (flattened rice or Aval), curd, and sooji. This idli will be soft and spongy, and it will pair well with any chutney and sambar. We'll share some ideas and ways along the way to help you prepare the extremely soft instant idli. Continue watching the video till the end to learn how to cook this delicious breakfast Instant idli. 

#instantidli #instantidlirecipe #vismaifood #pohaidli #ravaidli #ravaidlirecipe #idlirecipe #idlirecipeintelugu #spongyidli #softidli #smoothidli #idliandsambar #breakfast #breakfastrecipe #idliandchutney #vismaifoodrecipes 

This instant idli we made with poha and suji. You can try many varieties of idli like Oats idli, Ragi idli, Rava idli, sooji idli, poha idli, barley idli, jowar idli, millet idli, carrot idli, vegetable idli, red rice idli, brown rice idli, etc..

Don't forget to like, share and subscribe to Vismai Food channel : https://bit.ly/3Y5yPpc

Ingredients for Instant Idli:
1 cup Thick Poha
1.5 cups Sour Curd
½ tsp Cooking Soda
Add 1 cup Semolina(Rava)
½ cup Water
Salt to taste

Detailed recipes with Ingredients and Method in English & Telugu visit https://www.vismaifood.com/

ನೀವು ತ್ವರಿತ ಮತ್ತು ಸುಲಭವಾದ ಉಪಹಾರ ಪಾಕವಿಧಾನವನ್ನು ಹುಡುಕುತ್ತಿದ್ದೀರಾ? ಇಂದು ನಾವು ಮನೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಅತ್ಯಂತ ಮೃದುವಾದ ಮತ್ತು ಸ್ಪಂಜಿನ ತ್ವರಿತ ಇಡ್ಲಿಯನ್ನು ಹೇಗೆ ಮಾಡಬೇಕೆಂದು ನಿಮಗೆ ತೋರಿಸಲಿದ್ದೇವೆ. ಈ ತ್ವರಿತ ಇಡ್ಲಿಯನ್ನು ಪೋಹಾ (ಚಪ್ಪಟೆಯಾದ ಅಕ್ಕಿ ಅಥವಾ ಅವಲ್), ಮೊಸರು ಮತ್ತು ಸೂಜಿಯಂತಹ ಸರಳ ಪದಾರ್ಥಗಳೊಂದಿಗೆ ತಯಾರಿಸಲಾಗುತ್ತದೆ. ಈ ಇಡ್ಲಿ ಮೃದು ಮತ್ತು ಸ್ಪಂಜಿಯಾಗಿರುತ್ತದೆ ಮತ್ತು ಇದು ಯಾವುದೇ ಚಟ್ನಿ ಮತ್ತು ಸಾಂಬಾರ್‌ನೊಂದಿಗೆ ಚೆನ್ನಾಗಿ ಜೋಡಿಸುತ್ತದೆ. ಅತ್ಯಂತ ಮೃದುವಾದ ತ್ವರಿತ ಇಡ್ಲಿಯನ್ನು ತಯಾರಿಸಲು ನಿಮಗೆ ಸಹಾಯ ಮಾಡಲು ನಾವು ಕೆಲವು ವಿಚಾರಗಳು ಮತ್ತು ಮಾರ್ಗಗಳನ್ನು ಹಂಚಿಕೊಳ್ಳುತ್ತೇವೆ. ಈ ರುಚಿಕರವಾದ ಉಪಹಾರ ತ್ವರಿತ ಇಡ್ಲಿಯನ್ನು ಹೇಗೆ ಬೇಯಿಸುವುದು ಎಂದು ತಿಳಿಯಲು ವೀಡಿಯೊವನ್ನು ಕೊನೆಯವರೆಗೂ ನೋಡುವುದನ್ನು ಮುಂದುವರಿಸಿ.

வணக்கம் உணவுப் பிரியர்கள்!
விரைவான மற்றும் எளிதான காலை உணவு செய்முறையைத் தேடுகிறீர்களா? மிகவும் மென்மையான மற்றும் பஞ்சுபோன்ற உடனடி இட்லியை வீட்டிலேயே செய்வது எப்படி என்பதை இன்று நாங்கள் உங்களுக்குக் காண்பிக்கப் போகிறோம். இந்த உடனடி இட்லி போஹா (தட்டையான அரிசி அல்லது அவல்), தயிர் மற்றும் சூஜி போன்ற எளிய பொருட்களால் செய்யப்படுகிறது. இந்த இட்லி மென்மையாகவும், பஞ்சுபோன்றதாகவும் இருக்கும், மேலும் இது எந்த சட்னி மற்றும் சாம்பாருடன் நன்றாக இருக்கும். மிகவும் மென்மையான உடனடி இட்லியைத் தயாரிப்பதற்கு உங்களுக்கு உதவ சில யோசனைகளையும் வழிகளையும் நாங்கள் பகிர்ந்து கொள்வோம். இந்த சுவையான காலை உணவு உடனடி இட்லியை எப்படி சமைக்க வேண்டும் என்பதை அறிய வீடியோவை கடைசி வரை தொடர்ந்து பாருங்கள்.

మీరు శీఘ్ర మరియు సులభమైన అల్పాహారం వంటకం కోసం చూస్తున్నారా? ఈ రోజు మనం ఇంట్లోనే అత్యంత మృదువైన మరియు మెత్తటి తక్షణ ఇడ్లీని ఎలా తయారు చేయాలో మీకు చూపించబోతున్నాం. ఈ తక్షణ ఇడ్లీని పోహా (చదునైన అన్నం లేదా అవల్), పెరుగు మరియు సూజీ వంటి సాధారణ పదార్థాలతో తయారు చేస్తారు. ఈ ఇడ్లీ మెత్తగా మరియు మెత్తగా ఉంటుంది మరియు ఇది ఏదైనా చట్నీ మరియు సాంబార్‌తో బాగా జత అవుతుంది. చాలా మృదువైన తక్షణ ఇడ్లీని తయారు చేయడంలో మీకు సహాయపడటానికి మేము కొన్ని ఆలోచనలు మరియు మార్గాలను పంచుకుంటాము. ఈ రుచికరమైన అల్పాహారం ఇన్‌స్టంట్ ఇడ్లీని ఎలా ఉడికించాలో తెలుసుకోవడానికి వీడియోను చివరి వరకు చూడటం కొనసాగించండి.

en.title: Instant Idli | అతి మృదువైన ఇడ్లి 30 నిమిషాల్లో | Soft Idli Recipe | Vismai Food
en.description:
Instant Idli | chawal ke aate ki idli | Instant Idli Recipe | Instant Poha Idli | idli | idli recipe | Instant | idli without idli stand | Rava idli | idli recipe in telugu | idli banane ki recipe | idli recipe in telugu | idli batter recipe | idli chutney recipe |

Hello Foodies!
Are you looking for a quick and easy breakfast recipe? Today we're going to show you how to make an extremely soft and spongy instant idli at home. This instant idli is made with simple ingredients like as poha (flattened rice or Aval), curd, and sooji. This idli will be soft and spongy, and it will pair well with any chutney and sambar. We'll share some ideas and ways along the way to help you prepare the extremely soft instant idli. Continue watching the video till the end to learn how to cook this delicious breakfast Instant idli. 

#instantidli #instantidlirecipe #vismaifood #pohaidli #ravaidli #ravaidlirecipe #idlirecipe #idlirecipeintelugu #spongyidli #softidli #smoothidli #idliandsambar #breakfast #breakfastrecipe #idliandchutney #vismaifoodrecipes 

This instant idli we made with poha and suji. You can try many varieties of idli like Oats idli, Ragi idli, Rava idli, sooji idli, poha idli, barley idli, jowar idli, millet idli, carrot idli, vegetable idli, red rice idli, brown rice idli, etc..

Don't forget to like, share and subscribe to Vismai Food channel : https://bit.ly/3Y5yPpc

Ingredients for Instant Idli:
1 cup Thick Poha
1.5 cups Sour Curd
½ tsp Cooking Soda
Add 1 cup Semolina(Rava)
½ cup Water
Salt to taste

हेलो फूडीज़!
क्या आप एक त्वरित और आसान नाश्ता रेसिपी ढूंढ रहे हैं? आज हम आपको घर पर बेहद नरम और स्पंजी इंस्टेंट इडली बनाने का तरीका बताने जा रहे हैं। यह इंस्टेंट इडली पोहा (चपटा चावल या अवल), दही और सूजी जैसी सरल सामग्री से बनाई जाती है। यह इडली नरम और स्पंजी होगी और यह किसी भी चटनी और सांबर के साथ अच्छी लगेगी। बेहद नरम इंस्टेंट इडली तैयार करने में आपकी मदद के लिए हम कुछ विचार और तरीके साझा करेंगे। इस स्वादिष्ट नाश्ते की इंस्टेंट इडली को पकाने की विधि जानने के लिए वीडियो को अंत तक देखते रहें।

यह इंस्टेंट इडली हमने पोहा और सूजी से बनाई है। आप इडली की कई किस्में आज़मा सकते हैं जैसे ओट्स इडली, रागी इडली, रवा इडली, सूजी इडली, पोहा इडली, जौ इडली, ज्वार इडली, बाजरा इडली, गाजर इडली, सब्जी इडली, लाल चावल इडली, ब्राउन राइस इडली, आदि।

snippet.title: Dharambir Tau Interview | Viral Instagram Tau Ka Asli Sach | Real Face Ya Filter? | Ep 17 | MensXP
snippet.description:
In this episode of Men’s Locker Room, we’re in conversation with Dharambir Haryana aka Dharambir Tau. Taking Instagram by storm, Dharambir has been living every man’s dream life, with funny rants about children that give us Baghban 2.0 vibes. He believes in living his life to the fullest and enjoying every aspect of it, and brings loads of fun to the table in today’s conversation too. But who is the real Dharambir?

He talks about his persona on Instagram, and how there is a myth that old people can’t enjoy life, which he says shouldn’t be the case. If you’ve worked hard your entire life, you can and should be having fun with your earnings in your own favourite ways, irrespective of your age. He addresses why Dharambir Tau is the way he is on Instagram, and how he wants to set an example for everyone that age is just a number.

He also addresses the man and artist behind Dharambir, and urges everyone to focus on the message that he’s trying to deliver. He just wants people to be entertained by him, and the entertainment he does provide with the way he plays the games with Sadhika! To know more about the Real Dharambir and his truth, watch the full episode.

#MensLockerRoom #dharambir #dharambirharyana #interview #mensxp

snippet.description:

Tapu Sena has given everyone a surprise party which is a "Pav Bhaji Party", and everyone seems to be extremely happy and excited for the same, and relish the dish to the core. Stay tuned for more, watch now.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1790
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cQA3TWG8mHLCRO_vFhMoYiV

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 21 Teaser - 10th July 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 21 Teaser - 10th July 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Imran Abbas as Shani
Neelam Muneer as Shanzay
Nimra Khan as Sajeela
Mahmood Aslam as Kamran
Ismat Zaidi as Kulsoom
Maira Khan as Nadiya

Saqib Sameer as Khawar
Aadi Khan as Jugnu
Birjees Farooqui as Farzana
Farah Nadeem as Shakeela
Kinza Bukhari as Shazia
Mirza Rizwan as Faiq

snippet.title: #DoubleISMART Pooja Ceremony | Ram Pothineni | Puri Jagannadh | Charmme Kaur  | Puri Connects
snippet.description:
With the blessings of Lord Shiva 🔱
Ustaad RamPothineni & Dashing Director #PuriJagannadh's #DoubleISMART Pooja ceremony commenced 🪔 Shoot Begins on July 12th ❤️‍🔥

DoubleISMART, An Indian Action Entertainer film, written and directed by Puri Jagannnadh featuring Ram Pothineni in the lead role will be seen in a Massier character than iSmart Shankar. Produced by Puri Jagannadh and Charmme Kaur under Puri Connects, The film will have a much bigger span and will be made with a high budget on a large scale with top-class technical standards. Double iSmart will be releasing in Telugu, Tamil, Kannada, Malayalam, and Hindi languages for Maha Shivaratri on March 8, 2024.

snippet.title: Bike Servicing with Super Mechanics of Karol Bagh
snippet.description:
The Bharat Jodo Yatra is all about learning by listening to the voices of every section of India - lending an ear to the unheard stories of their struggles and triumphs. It is the confluence of these personal journeys with our unifying movement, the Bharat Jodo Yatra, which will help forge a better future for all.

The next pitstop of the Bharat Jodo Yatra was at the Biker's market in Karol Bagh, New Delhi where I met a group of ‘Super Mechanics’, and had candid conversations with these hard-working men who keep the wheels of Bharat moving.

I made an effort to understand the difficulties and learn about the dreams of mechanics in India. Many of them wanted to pursue studies during their younger days, but were forced by circumstances to become mechanics. They have given their best years to this profession. Some learnt the skills from their ‘Ustaads’, others were self-taught. Whatever course their lives took, through hard-work and dedication they have emerged as probably the best, though the most underrated motorcycle engineers in India. 

Umed Shah, a senior mechanic, taught me the nuances of servicing a bike. During our conversation, he told me how poverty had forced him to stop his studies and become a mechanic, like his elder brother. 

Two other ‘Super Mechanics’, Manoj Paswan and Vicky Sen told me the meagre returns of their profession worries them everyday because of the responsibilities of family life. Pressure to make ends meet, poor work conditions, lack of education and safety guidelines has caused serious health ailments to many - some diagnosed, but I fear many still remain undetected. 

Our mechanics toil to sustain the automobile industry - they deserve access to better facilities and the best opportunities. In the prosperity and well-being of every individual and the workers of every profession lies Bharat's true progress.

#rahulgandhi, #राहुल_गांधी, #bharatjodoyatra

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 20 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 10th July 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 20 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 10th July 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.title: बारिश में बनायें ये खास कुरकुरी चावल आलू की टिक्की व धनिये की चटनी। Quick n Easy Rice Potato Cutlets
snippet.description:
आलू-चावल की टिक्की, जो फटाफट बने, हर मौके के लिये परफेक्ट नाश्ता, Irresistible Appetizer for Parties, Mouthwatering Rice Potato Tikki, Perfect Snack for Any Occasion,Perfect Tea-Time Treat,the Perfect Blend of Flavors
#nashta #cutlets #tikki #streetfood 

𝐈𝐧𝐠𝐫𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐥𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐧 𝐑𝐚𝐰 𝐏𝐨𝐭𝐚𝐭𝐨 𝐓𝐢𝐤𝐤𝐢
𝑭𝒐𝒓 𝑫𝒐𝒖𝒈𝒉
चावल का आटा - Rice Flour - 1 cup
आलू - Potato - 3 nos (250 grams)
नमक  - Salt - 3/4 tsp
तेल - Oil 1 tsp
अदरक - Ginger - 1 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green Chilli - 1 tsp, chopped
चिल्ली फ्लेक्स - Chilli Flakes - 1/2 tsp
धनिया पाउडर - Cumin Powder - 1/2 tsp (roasted)
हरा धनिया - Coriander Leaves - 2 tbsp

𝑭𝒐𝒓 𝑪𝒉𝒖𝒕𝒏𝒆𝒚
हरा धनिया - Coriander Leaves - 1 cup
हरी मिर्च - Green Chilli - 2 nos
दही - Curd - 1/4 cup
अदरक - Ginger - 1 inch baton
काला नमक -Black Salt - 1/2 tsp 
नमक- Salt - 1/2 tsp
नमकीन - Namkeen - 2 tbsp

और तेल शेलो फ्राइ करने के लिये
and for shallow fry
Oil - 4 tbsp

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3819 | 10 July 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3819: Ek Bhayanak Sapna
--------------------------------------------------------
Sundar wakes Champaklal and Tapu awake in the middle of the night to talk about his situation. Sundar requests that Champaklal assist his friend financially. Sundar's friend owes someone a large sum of money and wants Bapuji to become the debtor. Sundar wishes to transport Champaklal and Tapu to Ahmedabad without informing Jetha. Chamapaklal agrees to assist Sundar, so everyone gets ready and boards the plane. Popatlal notices them leave Gokuldham and contacts Jetha to double-check. Jetha rushes to their aid. Watch the episode to find out if Jetha can stop Sundar!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3819, 10 July 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: PUBG Love Story : Pakistan के Karachi में जहां Seema Ghulam Haider रहती थी, वहां पहुंची बीबीसी टीम
snippet.description:
प्यार की ख़ातिर पहले पाकिस्तान से नेपाल और फिर भारत के ग्रेटर नोएडा में पहुंचीं सीमा गुलाम हैदर के पति का कहना है उन्होंने कोई तलाक़ नहीं दिया है और वो अपनी पत्नी-बच्चों को वापस चाहते हैं. कराची में जहां सीमा गुलाम हैदर रहा करती थीं, वहां बीबीसी की टीम पहुंची तो मकान मालिक ने बताया कि वो उनकी बेटी की तरह थी.

वीडियो: शुमाइला ख़ान, बीबीसी, कराची

#Pakistan #PUBG #IndiaPakistanLoveStory

* ऐसे ही और दिलचस्प वीडियो देखने के लिए चैनल सब्सक्राइब ज़रूर करें-
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCN7B-QD0Qgn2boVH5Q0pOWg?disable_polymer=true

* बीबीसी हिंदी से आप इन सोशल मीडिया चैनल्स पर भी जुड़ सकते हैं-

ABP আনন্দ বাংলা ও বাঙালির  সবথেকে নির্ভরযোগ্য সংবাদমাধ্যম। জেলা থেকে জেলা, রাজ্য থেকে দেশ, আবার সীমানা পেরিয়ে আন্তর্জাতিক - সবসময় সব খবর সবার আগে নির্ভুলভাবে তুলে ধরাই আমাদের লক্ষ্য। এগিয়ে থাকে এগিয়ে রাখে।

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: THE NUN II | OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
On September 8th, the greatest evil in the conjuring universe returns #TheNun2

New Line Cinema brings you the horror thriller “The Nun II,” the next chapter in the story of “The Nun,” the highest grossing entry in the juggernaut $2 billion “The Conjuring” Universe.

1956 – France. A priest is murdered. An evil is spreading. The sequel to the worldwide smash hit follows Sister Irene as she once again comes face-to-face with Valak, the demon nun.

Taissa Farmiga (“The Nun,” “The Gilded Age”) returns as Sister Irene, joined by Jonas Bloquet (“Tirailleurs,” “The Nun”), Storm Reid (“The Last of Us,” “The Suicide Squad”), Anna Popplewell (“Fairytale,” “The Chronicles of Narnia” trilogy) and Bonnie Aarons (reprising her role from “The Nun”), surrounded by an ensemble cast of international talent.

Michael Chaves (“The Conjuring: The Devil Made Me Do It”) directs, from a screenplay by Ian Goldberg & Richard Naing (“Eli,” “The Autopsy of Jane Doe”) and Akela Cooper (“M3GAN,” “Malignant”),with a story by Cooper, based on characters created by James Wan & Gary Dauberman.

The Safran Company’s Peter Safran and Atomic Monster’s James Wan produce, continuing their collaboration as filmmakers on all of the previous “Conjuring” films. “The Nun II” is executive produced by Richard Brener, Dave Neustadter, Victoria Palmeri, Gary Dauberman, Michael Clear, Judson Scott and Michael Polaire.
Joining Chaves behind the camera are director of photography Tristan Nyby (“The Conjuring: The Devil Made Me Do It,” “The Dark and the Wicked”), production designer Stéphane Cressend (“Les Vedettes,” “The French Dispatch”), editor Gregory Plotkin (2022’s “Scream,” “Get Out”), visual effects producer Sophie A. Leclerc (“Finch,” “Lucy”) and costume designer Agnès Béziers (“Oxygen,” “The Breitner Commando”), with composer Marco Beltrami (2022’s “Scream,” ”Venom: Let There Be Carnage”) providing the score.

“The Conjuring” Universe is the highest grossing horror franchise in history with $2+ billion worldwide. Globally, four of “The Conjuring” Universe titles have earned more than $300 million worldwide each (“The Nun,” $366 million; “The Conjuring 2,” $322 million; “The Conjuring,” $320 million; “Annabelle: Creation,” $307 million), and all seven have each grossed more than $200 million. “The Nun” is the top-earning film in the franchise, with more than $366 million worldwide.

New Line Cinema presents an Atomic Monster / Safran Company production, “The Nun II,” distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures. It is set to open in North America on September 8, 2023 and internationally beginning 6 September, 2023.

snippet.title: Yaar Ka Sataya Hua Hai | B Praak | Nawazuddin Siddiqui | Shehnaaz Gill | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies presents ‘Yaar Ka Sataya Hua Hai’, the second single from B Praak’s debut album, “Zohrajabeen”. Reuniting after their super hit 'Baarish Ki Jaaye', the all-star team of Nawazuddin Siddiqui, BPraak, Jaani, and Arvindr Khaira is back with yet another heart-wrenching song that explores the complexities of romance, and the pain of its absence. Experience a melancholic journey in the voice of BPraak paired with soul-stirring lyrics and composition by Jaani and a short film by Arvindr Khaira featuring Nawazuddin Siddiqui and Shehnaaz Gill that embodies a bittersweet tale that can't be chased anymore, painting a picture of respectful regret. Indulge your feelings in the beauty of this musical masterpiece, as it leaves you reflecting upon the significance of love and the poignancy of letting go. 

Listen to ‘Yaar Ka Sataya Hua Hai’ on your favourite streaming platform - https://umgindia.lnk.to/YKSHH

snippet.description:
Shiju Abdul Rasheed is an Indian actor who works in Malayalam and Telugu films. Shiju Abdul Rasheed is known by stage name Devi Shiju in Telugu films as Shiju Abdul Rasheed played a role in Kodi Ramakrishna's Devi. Shiju Abdul Rasheed has appeared in more than 50 films and several popular TV series. Shiju has a career that has spanned 14 years from Tollywood to Mollywood and on to an international movie. Shiju Abdul Rasheed was born on 4 August 1974 in Kerala, India. In 1996 was his debut and first success in a Tamil movie named Mahaprabhu, directed by A. Venkitesh. His performance as a villain in this movie gave him a major break in his career.

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Second Hand Car ख़रीदने चला Bhide | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Bhide Ki Car
snippet.description:
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Bhide's uncle owns mango farms. Since the sales of his mango's were quite profitable this year, he gifted 3 lakh rupees to Bhide. He is super excited about buying a new second-hand car with the money he received from his uncle. He approaches Sodhi and tells him about the same. Will Bhide's wish to buy a new car be fulfilled? Stay tuned to get your daily dose of laughter. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 3530
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of "Bhide Ki Car":
https://studio.youtube.com/playlist/PLSXTaG1fT0cRJaxqJOOo1wAulYwHYaMgd/edit

snippet.title: Bawaal - Official Teaser | Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
National Award Winners Sajid Nadiadwala & Nitesh Tiwari bring to you Bawaal on Prime Video
Presenting the official teaser of BAWAAL 
Varun Dhawan as Ajay Dixit 
Janhvi Kapoor as Nisha 
Produced by Sajid Nadiadwala 
Directed by Nitesh Tiwari 
Co-produced by Ashwiny Iyer Tiwari 
Written by Nitesh Tiwari, Nikhil Mehrotra, Piyush Gupta, Shreyas Jain, Ashwiny Iyer Tiwari 
A Nadiadwala Grandson Entertainment and EarthSky Pictures Production  
Music on T-series

Bawaal to release on Amazon Prime Video on 21st July 2023

Teaser Audio Credits:
Music Composed, Created & Arranged by Mithoon
Lyrics: Manoj Muntashir Shukla
Singer: Arijit Singh & Mithoon
Music Production: Godswill Mergulhao & Bobby Shrivastava
Music Assts: Anugrah, Godswill Mergulhao, Eli Rodrigues & Kaushal Gohil
Guitars: Kalyan Baruah
Woodwinds: ID Rao
Violin: Jeetu Thakur
Bass: Akashdeep Gogoi
Mix & Master: Eric Pillai @ Future Sound Of Bombay
Mix Asst: Michael Edwin Pillai

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

#janhvikapoor #varundhawan #nadiadwalagrandson #earthskynotes #ashwinyiyertiwari #mehrotranikhil #bawlekiduniya #wardakhannadiadwala #bawaalonprime
